## Limitations

### Using inline expression as an object key

- Object key can be an expression as long as it is wrapped in parentheses:
  ```terraform
  locals {
    foo = "bar"
    baz = {
      (format("key_prefix_%s", local.foo)) : "value"
      # format("key_prefix_%s", local.foo) : "value" this will fail
    }
  }
  ```
